 higher deities are of this kind. However, to the get the full =\r\nimpact of these mantras again lot of internal preparation is needed, for wi=\r\nthout preparation it is impossible to push the normal mind into these layer=\r\ns. Moreover it is not just the mind that must enter into these real spiritu=\r\nal planes, but even the pranamaya-kosha must also be lifted up to these pla=\r\nnes. This lifting of the pranamayakosha of a person is preceded by a releas=\r\ning of it normal functions - holding the frontal personality together***. I=\r\nn another language this\n is termed as releasing the Kundalini and rising it=\r\n upwards. Every time the pranamaya-kosha goes up to meet the energies of th=\r\ne spiritual plane, it also bring down a bit of those energies by associatio=\r\nn as it falls back. Incessantly done, it can eventually spiritualize and tr=\r\nansform the ordinary waking consciousness. A grand and worthy aim.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/spa=\r\nn&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Co=\r\nurier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: transparen=\r\nt; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, =\r\n0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,s=\r\nans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;But th=\r\ne bottomline remains, to use any mantra to its full benefit need lots of pr=\r\neparation. Rarely is it a one day job. A first vital step is to imbibe and =\r\ninstill a calmness in the whole being, which can lead to a stillness that i=\r\ns conducive for the\n mantra to show its real effects and let the body-mind =\r\nassimilate the same.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); fon=\r\nt-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif;=\r\n background-color: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=\r\n=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,courier,=\r\nmonaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: nor=\r\nmal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-fa=\r\nmily: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: tr=\r\nansparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;*** How and in what exact proportion and ma=\r\nnner the pranamayakosha of a person is released from its normal functions w=\r\nill vary from one sadhak to another. Just no hard fast rule. It can break o=\r\nff completely [from its ordinary engagements] in one shot in day one. Or it=\r\n can break of in parts and keep pushing up, eventually and if destined, for=\r\n the whole of it to\n get released from the job of integrating the surface p=\r\nersonality.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-f=\r\namily: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: t=\r\nransparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0=\r\n); font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-=\r\nserif; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;-Regards&lt;/div&gt;&lt;d=\r\niv style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,=\r\ncourier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-st=\r\nyle: normal;&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb=\r\n(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospa=\r\nce,sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;b=\r\nr&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-fam=\r\nily: Courier New,courier,monaco,monospace,sans-serif; background-color: tra=\r\nnsparent; font-st